Text: It's only 192 kbps or something, unfortunately. I hate it when people who uploads these things don't include the bitrate in info or the filename. I mean, how hard can it be to type it down...There's a FNT release in VBR V2 quality, which isn't so good either but it's the best one you can find for free.
It's also encoded with Fraunhofer rather than LAME. However, the music is lo-fi/garage style, so it's hard to tell an audible difference.
